#subtitle: Building relations with the other political parties of Germany.

= Inter-Party Relationships

Unlike our Norwegian and Swedish comrades, we've never had the luxury of an independent electoral majority, because of this weve historically needed the support of other parties.

- @liberals: Expand ties with Radikale Venstre.
- @bourgious: Attempt to repair relations with the bourgious parties.
- @sfrelation: Arrange a meeting with SF.
- @dkp: Approach the DKP.
- @spd_alone: We can stand alone for now.
- @easy_discard


