In secret we meet with [+ dkp_leader +], the leader of the danish communists, we agree with him that some joint events can take place at the grassroots level. 

Not much else is decided for now.

@dkp_rectification_of_history

The biggest stumbling block for our relations with the DKP have historically been their geopolitical support for the Soviet Union, as such most previous contacts have had to be held in secret. But our recent ideological shift against NATO have led to a warming of relations, as such the DKP uses the meeting to invite us to co-host an upcoming peace demonstration.

Under all circumstances – it would be necessary to make our relations public if we want to seek any further improvements in KPD relations.

- @yes_history: Yes, we will join them in the demonstration.
- @no_history: No, we politely decline for now.

